add table ip ferm
delete table ip ferm
add table ip ferm
add chain ip ferm INPUT { type filter hook input priority 0; }
add rule ip ferm INPUT tcp dport 22 accept
add table ip6 ferm
delete table ip6 ferm
add table ip6 ferm
add chain ip6 ferm INPUT { type filter hook input priority 0; }
add rule ip6 ferm INPUT tcp dport 22 accept
